cat << EOF
Spe is a Python IDE with auto-indentation, auto completion, call tips, syntax
coloring, syntax highlighting, UML, a class explorer, source index, an auto todo
list, sticky notes, integrated pycrust shell, a Python file browser, a recent
file browser, drag and drop, and context help. It also includes Blender support
a 3D object browser and the ability to run interactively inside Blender. It
includes the wxGlade GUI designer, the PyChecker source code doctor, and Kiki
regular expression console.
